# Step 2 — Ball Controller

Create:

```text
Scripts/Ball/BallController.cs
```

```csharp
using UnityEngine;

public class BallController : MonoBehaviour
{
    public Rigidbody rb;

    public void KickBall(Vector3 direction, float power)
    {
        rb.AddForce(direction * power, ForceMode.Impulse);
    }
}
```

